"width":525,"height":750,"file_path":"/8xIFjVLufLdUl8F0a7Odk3NOr5E.jpg","iso_639_1":"th","vote_average":0},{"width":619,"height":929,"file_path":"/tNgkjVR2a2iTUbpOqw0K2BQO1Pu.jpg","iso_639_1":"th","vote_average":0},{"width":525,"height":750,"file_path":"/uPUSI1d4DpCTmjoNhdPmQD99hkc.jpg","iso_639_1":"th","vote_average":0},{"width":746,"height":1049,"file_path":"/vX8ExbH0dMEUlBKNOZy81pC5zWg.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":0},{"width":525,"height":750,"file_path":"/xw0vxiZeag6pz3QQSqWqsU2gqBG.jpg","iso_639_1":"km","vote_average":0},{"width":540,"height":790,"file_path":"/du1s1HNQrSCzufoliULZmH2ygfC.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":0},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/pa568reI3gDG6HbxbuCjR1Pfcvf.jpg","iso_639_1":"cs","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/x7rTIi9QJDZ6B228IZwjad62RhT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/klM19fgDduzlIZYdlRgA0N0SU4c.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/btYu4D8a0Z172frk9FmkLy7cJrw.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:35:44.544+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Art of the Devil II","runtime":100,"tagline":"The Devil never leaves You Alive","homepage":"","overview":"Das Zusammentreffen von 6 alten Schulfreunden steht unter einem schlechten Stern. Ein dunkles Geheimnis ihrer Vergangenheit verbindet sie und führt sie in eine furchtbare Welt der schwarzen Magie und des Verderbens. Der Horror, den sie selbst ausgesät hatten, streckt nun gnadenlos seine Finger nach dem Leben der 6 aus, ohne ihnen eine Chance auf Erlösung zu geben."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Art of the Devil 2","runtime":102,"tagline":"The Devil never leaves You Alive.","homepage":"","overview":"A beautiful teacher is wronged by six of her students. Calling on demons and forces of black magic, she extracts an ultra-gruesome retribution against each of them."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"ลองของ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เรื่องราว เกี่ยวพันกับ ครูพนอ ครูสาวเสน่ห์แรง แม่เลี้ยงของ ต๊ะ เสน่ห์ของเธอ แรงจนชาย ที่อยู่รอบตัว ต่างพากัน หลงไหล และทำของ ใส่เธอ เพื่อให้เธอ หลงเ­สน่ห์ เมื่อการโดนของ เกิดขึ้นซ้ำแล้ว ซ้ำอีก จนทำให้ เธอเสียสติ เธอเปลี่ยนไป เป็นคนละคน จะเพี้ยน บ้าเหมือน คนโรคจิต ครูพนอพยายาม ที่จะเอา ของออกจาก ตัวเธอ โดยเดินทาง ไปหาหมอแขก เพื่อทำพิธีให้ ด้วยการกินเนื้อสดๆ ของผู้ที่ทำ ของใส่เธอ แต่เกิดความผิดพลาดแทนที่ ของจะออก จากตัวเธอ มันกลับส่งผล ทำให้เธอมีพลัง และอำนาจมากขึ้น เธอถลำลึก และหลับกลายเป็น ผู้หลงใหล ในไสยศาสตร์มนตร์ดำ นั้นเสียเอง และในค่ำคืนนี้ ครูพนอ จะใช้มนตร์ดำ กับ ลูกศิษย์ของเธอ และพาพวกเขา เข้าสู่โลกของ การชำระแค้น ด้วยไสยศาสตร์"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Art of the Devil 2","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Art of the Devil 2 explora a sedutora professora de uma escola primária chamada Sra. Panor. Cativados pela sua beleza e desesperados por ganhar o seu coração, muitos dos homens da vila simultaneamente fazem um feitiço de amor para ela. Mas aquela quantidade de feitiços foi demais para que uma só mulher aguentasse e a Sra. Panor começa a perder o contato com a realidade. Quando uma curandeira indígena lhe receita uma dieta de carne humana, a Sra. Panor mergulha ainda mais nas sombrias esquinas da feitiçaria. Com a ajuda da poderosa magia negra, a Sra. Panor precisa ter fé para conseguir a sua vingança contra os homens tomados pela luxúria que a levaram à beira da sanidade."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Art of the devil 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Cinq jeunes gens d'une vingtaine d'années partent dans une maison isolée pour l'enterrement du père de leur ami Ta. Ce dernier a vécu une adolescence difficile : après la mort de sa mère, son père s'est remarié avec une enseignante sexy nommée Panor qui n'hésitait pas à le frapper. Plus tard, Ta a dû surmonter une rupture avec la jolie Kim et la noyade de son frère qui le conduisit d'ailleurs en prison. Kim, son nouveau copain Por, le couple lesbien Tair et Noot et le comique de service Ko, débarquent donc la maison de Ta et, très vite, d'étranges événements surviennent. Des esprits maléfiques se manifestent et un passé traumatisant profondément enfoui refait surface alors qu'une malédiction décime la petite bande et que la vérité se révèle progressivement."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"A halál művészete 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hat jóbarát visszatér szülőfalujukba egyetemi tanítási szünet alatt. Itt találkoznak Miss Panor-al, aki egyből elbűvöli őket szépségével. A férfiak vetélkedni kezdenek a gyönyörű nőért, és céljuk érdekében mindent hajlandóak bevetni. Fekete mágiát használva megbabonázzák a nőt, aki kétségbeesetten igyekszik szabadulni a rábocsátott átok alól. De esélye nincs sok. Kétségbeesésében a fiatal nő egy indiai boszorkány doktor segítségét kéri. A dolgok azonban kicsúsznak az irányítása alól és Panor egy hatalmas erejű vodoo boszorkánnyá válik. Innentől kezdve már csak egy célja van az életében: bosszút állni azokon akik így elbántak vele..."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Art of the Devil 2","runtime":97,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La historia comienza con la reunión de seis estudiantes que años después de terminar con sus estudios deciden hacer una visita a su antigua maestra, a la que le causaron mala reputación por una broma de mal gusto. Ahora, ella conoce actos de magia negra y está dispuesta a vengarse de todo el daño que le hicieron sus ex-alumnos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"恶魔的艺术2：邪降","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　六个昔日的同窗好友在分开多年之后分别收到了旧时好友Ta的邀请，于是他们一起离开曼谷前往儿时的故乡。记忆之门也渐渐敞开。  　　当时还在读中学的他们与校内好色的体育老师不和，一次偶然的机会，六人撞破了体育老师与Ta的继母Panor（Mamee饰）的奸情，并用DV录下。Ta将此事告知父亲，导致父亲与继母panor的对峙，panor更加愤恨Ta。疯狂的体育老师遂将六人抓起来进行虐打侮辱。受辱后的六人愤恨难平，于是前去求助神奇的巫师，请求降邪......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chơi Ngải 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Art Of The Devil 2 là phần tiếp theo của bộ phim kinh dị kể về Ta và nhóm bạn học tình cờ biết được mẹ kế của Ta đang có gian tình với một giáo viên thể dục. Ta và các bạn tìm đến một thầy pháp trong vùng để nhờ ông làm phép nguyền rủa người giáo viên thể dục tàn ác. Thầy pháp đồng ý giúp họ, tuy nhiên cũng cảnh báo rằng nghiệp chướng có thể sẽ đeo bám họ mãi mãi. Giáo viên thể dục của họ đã phải chết trong đau đớn tột cùng bởi những chiếc móc câu. Bẵng đi một thời gian, nghiệp chướng không chịu buông tha họ. Nhóm bạn họp mặt để dự đám tang của bố Ta, và tấn thảm kịch đẫm máu bắt đầu từ đây..."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Voodoo: Umenie diabla 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Skupina mladých študentov sa vracia z Bangoku do svojho rodného mestečka. Stretávajú sa s ich bývalou učiteľkou a kamarátom Ta, ktorý ako jediný zostal v meste. Pri príchode domov sa nemôžu ubrániť vlne spomienok, ktoré ich pútajú k rodnému miestu. Aj keď sa všetci k sebe správajú priateľsky, niečo hrozivého z minulosti visí vo vzduchu. Prichádza vybavovanie účtov a odkrývanie toho, kto a ako sa v minulosti zaplietol s čiernou mágiou. Voodoo sa totiž nikdy nezbavíte a keď už ho nebudete potrebovať, bude sa vás držať až do hrobu."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Voodoo: Umění ďábla 2","runtime":100,"tagline":"Voodoo: Umění ďábla 2","homepage":"","overview":"Krvavý příběh pomsty a vražd zachycuje děsivé činy svůdné učitelky. Několik mužů z vesnice je očarováno její krásou a rozhodne se získat její srdce pomocí černé magie. Tolik kouzel najednou je ale příliš, učitelka brzy ztrácí pojem o realitě. Když jí indiánská čarodějnice předepíše jako lék lidské maso, propadá se ještě hlouběji. S pomocí šesti bývalých studentů se proto musí pokusit změnit svůj osud a pomstít se chtíčem posedlým mužům…"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"邪降：惡魔的藝術","runtime":102,"tagline":"泰國鬼片必看經典 重新定義恐怖","homepage":"","overview":"阿塔就讀中學時和一幫好友撞見自己的繼母和體育老師偷情，他告訴父親兩人的姦情，卻讓體育老師惱羞成怒，虐打羞辱眾人，不甘受辱的他們遂尋求巫師幫忙，請求降邪。多年後，逐漸淡忘此事的大家受阿塔邀請回老家重聚，開心的眾人陸續碰上無法解釋的怪事，沒人知道這次旅行的目的地是萬劫不復的人間煉獄…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Arte do Demônio 2","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O terror ganha uma nova explosão.... Arte do Demônio explora a sedutora professora de uma escola primária chamada Srta. Panor. Cativados por sua beleza e desesperados por ganhar seu coração, muitos dos homens do vilarejo simultaneamente fazem um feitiço de amor para ela. Mas aquela quantidade de feitiços foi demais para que uma só mulher aguentasse e a Srta. Panor começa a perder o contato com a realidade."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"악마의 기술 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"학교 친구들이 한 명의 아버지가 자살한 후 2년 만에 재회하는 이야기. 그들은 친구의 집에서 밤을 보내는데, 어둠이 내리면서 그들 각각에게 이상한 일들이 일어나기 시작하고, 이 모든 것은 마치 누군가가 그들에게 흑마술을 사용하는 것처럼 보이는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"De duivel laat je nooit levend achter.","homepage":"","overview":"Een groep middelbare schoolvrienden herenigt zich na twee jaar toen een van hun vaders zelfmoord pleegde. Ze brengen allemaal de nacht door bij hun vriend. Als de duisternis valt, gebeuren er één voor één vreemde dingen met hen. Het is alsof iemand de zwarte kunsten op hen gebruikt uit wraak voor een daad die deze groep vrienden samen op de middelbare school heeft begaan."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"邪降：惡魔的藝術","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"阿塔就讀中學時和一幫好友撞見自己的繼母和體育老師偷情，他告訴父親兩人的姦情，卻讓體育老師惱羞成怒，虐打羞辱眾人，不甘受辱的他們遂尋求巫師幫忙，請求降邪。多年後，逐漸淡忘此事的大家受阿塔邀請回老家重聚，開心的眾人陸續碰上無法解釋的怪事，沒人知道這次旅行的目的地是萬劫不復的人間煉獄…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":49236,"adult":false,"title":"Art of the Devil 3","video":false,"overview":"After Ta's mother is poisoned by his father, he finds himself in a dark and dangerous situation among demons when his family uses black magic to bring her back.","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3063,"vote_count":84,"poster_path":"/8adFAprCXfdAdlNYav0wa518iKK.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-03","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/3zUGPtZ4ET45JOdkdU9qddLjMNt.jpg","original_title":"ลองของ 2","original_language":"th"},{"id":1088080,"adult":false,"title":"Older Gods","video":false,"overview":"After the disappearance of his troubled friend, American Chris Rivers travels to the remote Welsh countryside to investigate what happened – leading him to a dark apocalyptic cult.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5252,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/tCL4U4nySiijUF2wTuB247KJbmT.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-01","vote_average":6.25,"backdrop_path":"/4jDbOf47uK86nuupSMDyYe5DOKF.jpg","original_title":"Older Gods","original_language":"en"},{"id":40127,"adult":false,"title":"Art of the Devil","video":false,"overview":"When Boom suffers abandonment and abuse by Prathan, she decides to use black magic to take revenge on him and his family.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0674,"vote_count":108,"poster_path":"/rxLlAzwihpsUQQXAbNVmKg2peBZ.jpg","release_date":"2004-06-17","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/tlVhygnHZIUcvMJnjRT7JZq0NqH.jpg","original_title":"คนเล่นของ","original_language":"th"},{"id":17157,"adult":false,"title":"Ace of Hearts","video":false,"overview":"Daniel Harding is a distinguished member of the K-9 police unit. His partner and best friend is Ace, a police dog. When Ace is accused of mauling a suspect, an overzealous DA convinces police authorities that Ace should be euthanized.","genre_ids":[18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4091,"vote_count":26,"poster_path":"/maWhGQkqwT0cuPLsCmhJpuyoGht.jpg","release_date":"2008-05-06","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/8DRNJbgA9Vgl0n06wiQvLWTpyZW.jpg","original_title":"Ace of Hearts","original_language":"en"},{"id":539220,"adult":false,"title":"Deva","video":false,"overview":"In the small Romanian town of Deva, Kato, a teen girl living in an orphanage, gets electrocuted while drying her hair. This apparently banal event will completely turn things upside down around her. The orphanage is invaded by electricians, and a new volunteer is hired to help restore order. Kato will become infatuated by her to the point of reconsidering the way she views her world.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1116,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/6IESojUkiiLSWBZ9CVEsmwvul9z.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-28","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Deva","original_language":"hu"},{"id":648990,"adult":false,"title":"La Casa","video":false,"overview":"Responding to an urgent call for help, a police officer becomes trapped by the evil spirits of a cursed house.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.756,"vote_count":96,"poster_path":"/fvTGWaQejnHQBZbEOrdbb38NBTC.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-30","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/kLsrE6q4ld144ECBkydZ4dV8t9T.jpg","original_title":"La casa","original_language":"es"},{"id":503902,"adult":false,"title":"Sabrina","video":false,"overview":"A toy manufacturer and his wife are terrorized by a demon after their orphaned niece tries to call her late mother's spirit.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0174,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/zheAqvuUgk9L2ElLHgYo92WJIdO.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-12","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/rXA03j9HBzhcmgjJetcVSjkmwQg.jpg","original_title":"Sabrina","original_language":"id"},{"id":645856,"adult":false,"title":"The Seventh Day","video":false,"overview":"A renowned exorcist teams up with a rookie priest for his first day of training. As they plunge deeper into hell on earth, the lines between good and evil blur, and their own demons emerge.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6046,"vote_count":287,"poster_path":"/dtt2dfMdmlCcgaJZkPPQsIY5oR6.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-26","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/xH23sRbfMtwZ2oBtBf607VUNrGt.jpg","original_title":"The Seventh Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":15762,"adult":false,"title":"Night of the Creeps","video":false,"overview":"In 1959, an alien experiment crashes to earth and infects a fraternity member. They freeze the body, but in the modern day, two geeks pledging a fraternity accidentally thaw the corpse, which proceeds to infect the campus with parasites that transform their hosts into killer zombies.","genre_ids":[27,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2876,"vote_count":554,"poster_path":"/A3s2tQGNb6mhlr1hPZeE5F8IUwp.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-21","vote_average":6.712,"backdrop_path":"/rKr2NzAvxlTDCI7iSSNLaCXt0Aj.jpg","original_title":"Night of the Creeps","original_language":"en"},{"id":20544,"adult":false,"title":"Something the Lord Made","video":false,"overview":"A dramatization of the relationship between heart surgery pioneers Alfred Blalock and Vivien Thomas.","genre_ids":[10770,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7572,"vote_count":294,"poster_path":"/lk2wEO6Rt3mnZmfRTu8wvYiGPmp.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-30","vote_average":7.871,"backdrop_path":"/oT6z05HLXAfgD2CI3cPMuqG8OAW.jpg","original_title":"Something the Lord Made","original_language":"en"},{"id":119698,"adult":false,"title":"The Dinosaur Project","video":false,"overview":"Found footage of an expedition into the Congo jungle where a team of explorers stumbles upon a colony of Dinosaurs.","genre_ids":[12,28,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0285,"vote_count":324,"poster_path":"/qmMoPP8hSFbxzLn3Tt9UonPsma9.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-09","vote_average":5.782,"backdrop_path":"/nAhKxK8inVjHeHAw6W2xkQjdbh5.jpg","original_title":"The Dinosaur Project","original_language":"en"},{"id":431937,"adult":false,"title":"Mr & Mme Adelman","video":false,"overview":"How did Sarah and Victor get along for more than 45 years? Who was this enigmatic woman living in the shadow of her husband? Love, ambition, betrayals and secrets feed the story of this extraordinary couple, as they experience both the large and small moments of the last century's history.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7697,"vote_count":458,"poster_path":"/eElm9ZjbKy7JOeiz3GxrTK6mJss.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-08","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/uyYgW4aUwGRh2pdyMgNfeqBC0Jc.jpg","original_title":"Mr & Mme Adelman","original_language":"fr"},{"id":41428,"adult":false,"title":"Tetsuo: The Iron Man","video":false,"overview":"A \"metal fetishist\", driven mad by the maggots wriggling in the wound he's made to embed metal into his flesh, runs out into the night and is accidentally run down by a Japanese businessman and his girlfriend. The pair dispose of the corpse in hopes of quietly moving on with their lives. However, the businessman soon finds that he is now plagued by a vicious curse that transforms his flesh into iron.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4846,"vote_count":686,"poster_path":"/9RquCMBJ42Kq7ASBy0qcyVP0ugi.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-01","vote_average":6.984,"backdrop_path":"/xt75NSIlfzwPwuBsuarB3i1mBxj.jpg","original_title":"鉄男","original_language":"ja"},{"id":290637,"adult":false,"title":"Pay the Ghost","video":false,"overview":"One year after his young son disappeared during a Halloween carnival, Mike Cole is haunted by eerie images and terrifying messages he can’t explain. Together with his estranged wife, he will stop at nothing to unravel the mystery and find their son—and, in doing so, he unearths a legend that refuses to remain buried in the past.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1185,"vote_count":798,"poster_path":"/iHG1QcxaRCiFIdSK1HZA6zOEFsl.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-16","vote_average":5.38,"backdrop_path":"/hHwuzYiWtwxUw5Jf1Ue3ZPn04Vt.jpg","original_title":"Pay the Ghost","original_language":"en"},{"id":44363,"adult":false,"title":"Frozen","video":false,"overview":"When three skiers find themselves stranded on a chair lift at a New England ski resort that has closed for the next week, they are forced to make life or death choices that prove to be more perilous than staying put and freezing to death.","genre_ids":[53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.1318,"vote_count":1965,"poster_path":"/2J3URUnDrIpNvh0uVqINQvr4HhW.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-05","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/vD1yKObsRS2cvpmtuaCaMhr4zxe.jpg","original_title":"Frozen","original_language":"en"},{"id":13027,"adult":false,"title":"Eagle Eye","video":false,"overview":"Jerry Shaw and Rachel Holloman are two strangers whose lives are suddenly thrown into turmoil by a mysterious woman they have never met. Threatening their lives and family, the unseen caller uses everyday technology to control their actions and push them into increasing danger. As events escalate, Jerry and Rachel become the country's most-wanted fugitives and must figure out what is happening to them.","genre_ids":[9648,53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":